#summary Data types supported by CIF

= Data types supported by CIF =

By default CIF supports the following primary data types for queries or feeds:
 # IP address
 # Domain / FQDN
 # URI
 # CIDR
 # Email address
 # Malware hash
  * (_must be enabled in feed config_)
 # UUID
  * (_generally used by the API_)

== Feed Examples ==

You can find example feeds [http://code.google.com/p/collective-intelligence-framework/wiki/Feeds here].
